metadata.name: Astro Baby Club #1
metadata.description: Astro Baby Club is a collection of uniquely hand-drawn NFTs generated on the Ethereum galaxy. ABC was founded with the core mission of doing good, having fun, and pushing the limits of web3. Each NFT is a forever membership in the Astro Baby Club which grants access to member benefits starting with in-person and online events, merchandise, IP ownership of your unique NFT, and more. Check www.AstroBabyClub.com for more details.
